    <h2><span class="num">1</span> Introduction &amp; Scope</h2>
    <p>This Privacy Policy describes how <strong class="w">Nextintinc</strong> ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, processes, and protects your personal information when you use the <strong class="w">Rummy Jodi</strong> mobile application ("App"). This policy applies to all users of Rummy Jodi and complies with:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Information Technology Act, 2000</li>
      <li>IT (Intermediary Guidelines and Digital Media Ethics Code) Rules, 2021</li>
      <li>Digital Personal Data Protection (DPDP) Act, 2023</li>
      <li>Applicable Indian gaming and tax regulations</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin-top:10px">By using the App, you consent to the practices described in this policy.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- 2 -->
  <div class="sec">
