    </div>
    <ul style="margin-top:12px">
      <li>Location is checked only at app launch</li>
      <li>Location data is <strong class="w">NOT stored on our servers</strong> beyond this single eligibility check</li>
      <li>We do not track your movements</li>
      <li>Location is never used for advertising targeting</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

